        "text": "6. Young—Greek, \"The younger men.\"",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "sober-minded—self-restrained [Alford]. \"Nothing is so hard at this age as to overcome pleasures and follies\" [Chrysostom].",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
